name: KING OF THE SEA
description:
God of the first generation of Olympus, rules the waters and all its creatures.

Protector of fishermen and sailors.

An unpredictable and temperamental king, a great ally when harmony reigned but a great enemy if he was challenged.

With a single movement of his powerful trident he could cause great catastrophes, he was called the shaker of the earth.

He's Neptune
